$interpreted: Big-Horn-Dora: I wonder how that dispatch mission is going...
Guard-Dora: What are you worried about? It only just started! Puggi'll do it for sure!
Carrot-Dora: We've got a problem!
Carrot-Dora: This doofus just told me that because we didn't have enough food, he gave empty rations to the dispatch team!
Guard-Dora: What!? Now they've got no food!? Are they gonna fail?
Big-Horn-Dora: (I'll have to bring over that food I hid...)
Puggi: You guys are just too amazing! Win after win after win, this mission'll be a cinch!
Puggi: And resting, of course, just reaps us rewards down the line!
Puggi: So, everyone rest up!
Puggi: Haw... shoo...
Mandora: I'm hungry!
Puggi: Whoa, hands off the horns!
Guard-Dora: We're hungry!
Puggi: Alright, this is no time for jokes!
Big-Horn-Dora: Let go of Puggi! I have food!
Mandora: Yay! That looks more tasty!
Guard-Dora: We won't starve!
Puggi: Oof, I thought the curtain was about to close for the last time, ladies and gents!
Puggi: Way to earn your keep, side character! I see you were hiding food just so you could save the day!
Big-Horn-Dora: Uh... I...
Puggi: Well, you did it! Enjoy your time in the spotlight!
Puggi: I bet we'll make a leader out of you yet!
Big-Horn-Dora: But... I've never even been on a mission. Could I really be a leader?
Puggi: Hmm... I guess we'll have to bring you on a mission, then!
Big-Horn-Dora: Yay!
Puggi: First, we dine!
Puggi: Eat up and gather your strength, little ones!
Puggi: We've already run into some difficulties during this mission, and yet...
Puggi: We should all thank our friend here for stepping in and saving the day!
Mandora: Big Horn! Big Horn!
Puggi: Growing up so fast, making a leader of himself... I just know one day he'll make a fantastic... sidekick!!
Big-Horn-Dora: I'll be the best sidekick there is!
Mandora: Sidekick! Sidekick! Sidekick!
Puggi: Let me make an official announcement right here, right now!
Puggi: With me, you lot, and Mr. Sidekick here...
Puggi: This mission will be a huge success!!
